Based on web search, here are key character inspirations for Asa:

BEST CHARACTER PARALLELS:
1. LUCY (Elfen Lied)
Why this works:

Split personality (innocent girl / ruthless killer)
Dissociative Identity Disorder due to trauma
Society rejected her (Diclonius persecution)
Transformation isn't physical - it's psychological
Both personalities exist simultaneously

What we take:

Trauma-based split (bullying/isolation creates second personality)
Innocent base / ruthless alt (perfect for Asa)
Society created the monster (not born evil)


2. TOUKO FUKAWA / GENOCIDER SYO (Danganronpa)
Why this works:

Shy, stuttering writer (Touko)
Becomes confident, violent serial killer (Genocider Syo)
Triggered by specific stimulus (sneezing/stress)
Split personality has opposite traits

What we take:

Trigger mechanism (Asa's Vestige activates under specific conditions)
Opposite personalities (timid → manipulative)
Physical tell (something changes when switch happens)


3. MARI/KOMORI (Inside Mari)
Why this works:

College dropout loner (socially invisible)
Created alternate personality from unresolved trauma
Identity crisis (who am I really?)
Mother's emotional abuse → dissociation

What we take:

Social outcast origin (bullied, ignored, invisible)
Personality created as coping mechanism
Trauma from parental/societal pressure


4. SAWAKO KURONUMA (Kimi ni Todoke)
Why this works:

Shrinking Violet archetype
Nicknamed after horror character (Sadako)
Wants friendship desperately but can't make connections
Resemblance to scary character = ostracized

What we take:

Yearns for connection (not antisocial by choice)
Misunderstood by peers (seen as creepy/weird)
Gentle soul crushed by social rejection


5. MEGUMI SHIMIZU (Shiki) - POST-TRANSFORMATION
Why this works:

Human → vampire (Shiki)
Personality changes drastically
Manipulates former friends
Bitter about village life → takes revenge

What we take:

Transformation unlocks hidden resentment
Uses manipulation strategically
Revenge against those who ignored her


ASA'S CHARACTER SYNTHESIS:
BASE PERSONALITY (Timid Asa):

Inspired by: Sawako Kuronuma, Touko Fukawa
Traits:

Painfully shy, apologizes constantly
Walks with head down, avoids eye contact
Brilliant (academically) but socially invisible
Desperately wants to be seen/heard
Kind-hearted but crushed by rejection



VESTIGE PERSONALITY (Manipulative Asa):

Inspired by: Lucy (Elfen Lied), Genocider Syo, Megumi Shimizu
Traits:

Confident, sharp-tongued, cocky
Enjoys exposing hypocrisy
Manipulates conflicts (puppeteer energy)
Not evil—just brutally honest
Finds humanity's contradictions amusing




ASA'S COMPLETE PROFILE:
Name: Asa (朝 - "Morning")
Age: 20-21
Gender: Female
Appearance (Base):

Plain, forgettable (literally blends into background)
Glasses (hides behind them)
Long hair covering face
Slouched posture (trying to be smaller)
Wears oversized clothes (wants to disappear)

Appearance (Vestige Active):

Stands straight (confident posture)
Hair pushed back (no longer hiding)
