Bullied throughout school (awkward, nerdy, loner)
Parents pressured her to "be normal" (rejected her interests)
No friends (people avoided her, thought she was creepy)
Breaking point: [We need to define this]
Vestige born from: Social rejection + suppressed rage

The Vestige (Split Personality):

Everything Asa wanted to be but couldn't
Confident, witty, fearless
Says things Asa thinks but never voices
Not cruel—just unfiltered truth
Enjoys watching people squirm when exposed

Philosophy:

Base Asa: "I just want to be accepted..."
Vestige Asa: "They don't deserve acceptance. Let them taste their own medicine."


ASA'S POWER (BASED ON PHILOSOPHY):
"MIRROR TRUTH" - Forces people to confront themselves
Ability:

When Vestige active: Asa can make people speak their hidden thoughts
Strips away social masks
Exposes hypocrisy, lies, secret resentments
Creates conflicts by revealing truth

How It Works:

Touch someone OR speak to them directly
They involuntarily voice what they're really thinking
Can't stop themselves (truth forced out)
Lasts 30 seconds to 5 minutes

Example:

Person acting nice → forced to admit "I hate you"
Perpetrator lying → forced to confess crime
Haruto/Koyoi arguing → forces them to voice their deepest beliefs → conflict escalates


